Name: DinoScape
About the game: As a brave caveman, save the dinosaurs from extinction! Try to escape from meteorids, lava, sharp teeth and deep abysses together with your riding dinosaur. Collect rare dinosaur eggs. Collect emeralds and unlock chic accessories. Dinoscape was launched by Tomary in 2020. Have fun with DinoScape! Tomary
